#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.78"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.78:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.78:0.2"
msgid "8. Ānandavagga"
msgstr "8. Ānanda"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.78:0.3"
msgid "78. Sīlabbatasutta"
msgstr "78. Precepts and Observances"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.225"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.78:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ "
"bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one "
"side. The Buddha said to him:"

msgctxt "an3.78:1.2"
msgid ""
"“sabbaṃ nu kho, ānanda, sīlabbataṃ jīvitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ upaṭṭhānasāraṃ "
"saphalan”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Ānanda, are all precepts and observances, lifestyles, and spiritual paths "
"fruitful when taken as the essence?”"

msgctxt "an3.78:1.3"
msgid "“Na khvettha, bhante, ekaṃsenā”ti."
msgstr "“This is no simple matter, sir.”"

msgctxt "an3.78:1.4"
msgid "“Tena hānanda, vibhajassū”ti."
msgstr "“Well then, Ānanda, break it down.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: Yañhissa → yathārūpaṃ hissa (?)
msgctxt "an3.78:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Yañhissa, bhante, sīlabbataṃ jīvitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ upaṭṭhānasāraṃ sevato "
"akusalā dhammā abhivaḍḍhanti kusalā dhammā parihāyanti, evarūpaṃ sīlabbataṃ "
"jīvitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ upaṭṭhānasāraṃ aphalaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Take the case of someone who cultivates precepts and observances, a "
"lifestyle, and a spiritual path, taking this as the essence. If unskillful "
"qualities grow while skillful qualities decline, that’s not fruitful."

#. VAR: Yañca khvāssa → yañca khvassa (s1-3) | yañhissa (mr) | yathārūpañca khvāssa (?)
msgctxt "an3.78:2.2"
msgid ""
"Yañca khvāssa, bhante, sīlabbataṃ jīvitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ upaṭṭhānasāraṃ "
"sevato akusalā dhammā parihāyanti, kusalā dhammā abhivaḍḍhanti, evarūpaṃ "
"sīlabbataṃ jīvitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ upaṭṭhānasāraṃ saphalan”ti."
msgstr ""
"However, if unskillful qualities decline while skillful qualities grow, that "
"is fruitful.”"

msgctxt "an3.78:2.3"
msgid "Idamavoca āyasmā ānando."
msgstr "That’s what Ānanda said,"

msgctxt "an3.78:2.4"
msgid "Samanuñño satthā ahosi."
msgstr "and the teacher approved."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.78:3.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando “samanuñño me satthā”ti, uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi."
msgstr ""
"Then Ānanda, knowing that the teacher approved, got up from his seat, bowed, "
"and respectfully circled the Buddha, keeping him on his right, before "
"leaving."

msgctxt "an3.78:3.2"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā acirapakkante āyasmante ānande bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr ""
"Then, not long after Ānanda had left, the Buddha addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "an3.78:3.3"
msgid "“sekho, bhikkhave, ānando;"
msgstr "“Mendicants, Ānanda is a trainee,"

msgctxt "an3.78:3.4"
msgid "na ca panassa sulabharūpo samasamo paññāyā”ti."
msgstr "but it’s not easy to find his equal in wisdom.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.78:3.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
